# driver7-x86-withoutdbg.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png) 


### Description

driver7-x86-withoutdbg.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: d9f2c3d6-160c-4eb3-8547-894fcf810342
- **Created**: 2023-01-09
- **Author**: Michael Haag

